<p><span><strong><span>招聘岗位</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>此次联合招聘</span></p>
<p><span>共有256个岗位拟聘282人</span></p>
<p><span>其中</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/56119b3da0704d6c9bb901b6638dc7e9.jpeg" /></p>
